OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Whoopi Goldberg has been suspended from
OL,6, a US talk show after saying the        
OL,7, Holocaust involved "two groups of white
OL,8, people".                               
OL,10,FABC News said Goldberg would be off-air
OL,11,Ffor two weeks after her "wrong and     
OL,12,Fhurtful comments".                     
OL,14,FThe actress and TV personality said on 
OL,15,FABC's The View that the Nazi genocide  
OL,16,Fof the Jews was "not about race".      
OL,18,FShe apologised but then caused further 
OL,19,Foffence while attempting to explain her
OL,20,Fremarks on a late-night show.          
